by a parent
Saturday, February 13, 2010
EDHS is a joke! They are only concerned with filling the school with bodies to get more state money. There is no support from the administration for the teachers who have to deal with these students that no other school wants, which is why many "good" students leave. The new principal only taught for a year and a half and does not even have an adminstrator certificate. He has been overheard making racial slurs about the students, and constantly compares his own two "white" children with the EDHS students and tells them how they will never amount to anything compared to his kids. The new assistant principal taught social studies for two years and is the football coach. What a coincidence. Atheletes are given full reign of the school, where as non atheletes are dealt with a lot harsher. The focus is on sports not academics, and if you are looking for a place for your student to get a good education, do not send them there!
